name: 106-map-outline
title: Map
description: What you're looking for... It's not on any map! Unless it is! This animated icon represents the map.

name: 1352-track-order-outline
title: Track order
description: Ever since they sent her package, she kept tracking its location every other hour. This animated icon stands for tracking an order.

name: 18-location-pin-outline
title: Location pin
description: Can't you pinpoint your location? Use this animated icon to illustrate your geographical position.

name: 1981-africa-continent-outline
title: Africa
description: Africa is a continent of wonderful diversity: it has 54 countries but  more than 3,000 tribes. This Lottie animation illustrates Africa.

name: 52-location-pin-on-square-map-outline
title: Location pin
description: The world's yours to explore! Where will you go? This animated icon allows for describing your location.

name: 53-location-pin-on-round-map-outline
title: Location pin
description: Where are you now? You can show your location on the map with a beautifully animated icon.

name: 730-signpost-direction-outline
title: Sign
description: Are we going in the right direction? We're looking for Neverland. This animated icon illustrates a direction signpost.

name: 735-world-globe-outline
title: Globe
description: She thought: what to give a man who has everything? She gave him the world. This animated icon illustrates a globe.

name: 740-road-sign-signpost-direction-outline
title: Road sign
description: Direction? Neverland. We really don't want to grow up. This animated icon illustrates a road signpost.

name: 74-navigation-outline
title: Navigation
description: With good navigation, you'll never end up on a bad station. This animated icon represents the navigation sign.

name: 754-pin-attachement-outline
title: Pin
description: Then she sang: no, you can't pin me down. This animated icon illustrates a pin attachment.

name: 85-navigation-alone-outline
title: Navigation
description: With navigation by your side, you'll never get lost! This animated icon illustrates the sign of navigation.

name: 86-compass-outline
title: Compass
description: Let your heart be your compass when you're lost! This animated icon illustrates a compass for every hiking trip.

name: 922-highway-outline
title: Highway
description: The highway don't care If you're coming home, but I do. This animated icon illustrates a highway.
